	 * The block converts wide table and toolbar layouts into stacked card-like
	 * flows, adjusts modal/command surfaces for viewport-height constraints,
	 * preserves touch target sizes, and constrains overflow for panel chrome.
	 *
	 * @return string CSS emitted for mobile and touch-oriented panel layouts.
	 */
